NAME

	Scalar::Util::Ref - A selection of general-utility reference subroutines

SYNOPSIS

	use Scalar::Util::Ref qw(:all);

DESCRIPTION

	This module provides general utilities for references and object references.

	See "perldoc Scalar::Util::Ref" for the rest of the document.

DEPENDENCIES

	perl 5.8.1 or later, and a C compiler.

INSTALLATION

	To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

